ge Program in which they are participating. Students participating in Exchange Programs in all fields are eligible. Candidates must not have previously received a Nuveen International Award. Awards presume that nominees are in good academic standing.  Thank you for your interest in the John and Grace Nuveen International Awards.  The application period for academic year 2016-2017 is now closed.   Congratulations to Our Current Awardees:   Awardees  2016-2017  Naheed Ahmad  Adam Batton  Ana Criollo  David Dominguez  Kristine Guliana  Spyridon Hasiakos  Jessica Hyker  Daniel Rosales  Dominika Struk              © Copyright 2014-2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois      Footer Navigation   University of Illinois Hospital & Health Sciences System Fulbright Google Translate Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Privacy Policy  Contact Us           Cookie Settings   